<div class="col-md-8">
<div class ="sellheader text-center">
		Please follow the instruction for uploading the data regarding the items.Provide the complete description 
		and please provide all the features. 
					
		
	</div>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-2"></div>
<div class="col-md-8">
		
	<br>
